name: Honeysuckle Face & Body Oil 4oz
description: Rejuvenate and renew your skin with Honeysuckle Face & Body Oil. This luxurious oil blends together nourishing Honeysuckle Extract, Chamomile, and Babassu Seed Oil to provide deep hydration while combating signs of aging. Experience fast-absorbing moisture that soothes and comforts dry, flaky, or irritated skin. Perfect for all skin types, this product should be used in the morning and evening after bathing to apply a few drops at a time on damp skin for the best results. Protect yourself against free radicals with antioxidant defense and prevent visible signs of aging by adding Honeysuckle Face & Body Oil into your daily skincare routine. Ingredients: Glycine Soja (Soybean) Oil, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Rosa Rubigenosa Seed Oil (Rose Hip), Tocopherol, Fragrance, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice (Aloe Vera), Lavandula Angustifolia (Lavender) Oil, Chamomilla Recutita (Matricaria) Flower Oil, Orbignya Oleifera (Babassu) Seed Oil.
